snippet.title: Ghostrunner 2 - Demo Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Jack is back and upgraded! Be one of the first to try Jack's new arsenal as you put your cyber ninja katana and motorbike skills to the test with the newly announced Ghostrunner 2 Demo. 

Download the Ghostrunner 2 Demo and Pre-order on PlayStation 5 Today. Upgrade to the Deluxe or Brutal Edition for even more Ghostrunner 2 content!
